---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---
<Base title="Refund policy" description="14-day satisfaction window on every manual sold at strmanuals.com." path="/refund">
  <section class="container-page py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto measure">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-6">Policy</p>
      <h1 class="mb-10">Refund policy.</h1>

      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        If a manual didn't help you, email us within 14 days of purchase and we'll
        refund you. No interrogation, no forms, no "tell us why." We don't want
        money from someone who didn't get value.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        Refunds process back to the original card within 3–5 business days via
        Stripe. Your download access is revoked at the same time.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--color-mute);">
        Email <a href="mailto:hello@strmanuals.com" class="underline">hello@strmanuals.com</a> with
        your order number to start. That's the whole process.
      </p>

      <p class="text-caption font-mono mb-10" style="color: var(--color-mute);">
        Last updated <time datetime={today}>{today}</time>
      </p>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">A note on bundles</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Bundle refunds are all-or-nothing — you can't keep three manuals and refund two.
        If you only want a partial refund on the 5-manual bundle, we'll refund the full bundle
        and you can re-buy individual manuals at list price. Once you've downloaded 3 or more
        of the included manuals, the bundle is non-refundable but we'll still help if the
        issue is technical.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">A note on download links</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Your download link is HMAC-signed and expires 24 hours after issuance. If your link
        expires before you download, email us — we'll send a fresh one. That's a delivery
        issue, not a refundable one.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Chargebacks</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        If you initiate a chargeback through your bank without contacting us first, account
        access is suspended pending review. Email is faster and easier than a chargeback —
        and we approve all reasonable refund requests within the 14-day window.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
